===Noun===
'''attention'''  (''[[uncountable]]'')
# Mental focus.
#: ''Please direct your '''attention''' to the following words.''
# For military personnel, a state of alertness in the standing position.
#: ''The company will now come to '''attention'''.''
# (Advertising) a rating used to measure a commercial's ability to stand out from the clutter of all other ads on TV, in advertising research.
#: ''* The beer commercial with blonde twins had a higher attention score than the one showing a family enjoying slipcovers.''

